main event: A farmer observed a large, luminous bell-shaped object descend into his field in Gills Rock, Wisconsin.
interesting points: The object was approximately 30 feet in diameter,The reporting officer experienced intense heat and glare when attempting to approach the object,The object rose straight up and accelerated rapidly out of sight,No evidence or clues were found regarding the object's origin or nature,The case has been classified as UNIDENTIFIED.
